1
00:00:06,300 --> 00:00:07,241
Let's go to a PC bang.

2
00:00:07,241 --> 00:00:08,153
No.

3
00:00:08,153 --> 00:00:08,887
Wanna play League of Legends?

4
00:00:08,887 --> 00:00:09,660
No.

5
00:00:09,660 --> 00:00:10,413
A league match?

6
00:00:10,413 --> 00:00:11,131
No.

7
00:00:11,131 --> 00:00:12,079
What about Overwatch?

8
00:00:12,080 --> 00:00:13,080
No.

9
00:00:13,728 --> 00:00:15,435
Huh? That's...

10
00:00:15,436 --> 00:00:17,838
Wait, is that Jihan?

11
00:00:26,473 --> 00:00:27,627
Wait.

12
00:00:37,030 --> 00:00:38,869
- Hey, what are you doing?
- Hey, hey, hey!

13
00:00:38,870 --> 00:00:41,879
Nope~ not happening.

14
00:00:41,880 --> 00:00:45,644
So why is our dear
freshman sleeping out here?

15
00:00:45,645 --> 00:00:48,327
Ah... I got kicked out.

16
00:00:48,328 --> 00:00:49,555
Kicked out?

17
00:00:49,556 --> 00:00:50,683
Of your house?

18
00:00:50,684 --> 00:00:51,689
Why?

19
00:00:51,690 --> 00:00:53,249
I... don't really know.

20
00:00:53,250 --> 00:00:55,348
When can you go back home?

21
00:00:55,349 --> 00:00:57,658
I don't really know that either...

22
00:00:58,980 --> 00:01:01,179
Then you've been sleeping here every day?

23
00:01:01,180 --> 00:01:03,803
Pretty much...

24
00:01:05,900 --> 00:01:08,189
Then you can stay at Hyunjun's place.

25
00:01:08,190 --> 00:01:10,137
He lives alone near campus

26
00:01:10,138 --> 00:01:12,472
I've crashed there a few times myself,

27
00:01:12,473 --> 00:01:15,222
and it's decent. Pretty clean too.

28
00:01:15,662 --> 00:01:17,380
More importantly,

29
00:01:17,381 --> 00:01:19,199
what kind of senior would allow

30
00:01:19,200 --> 00:01:22,749
his junior to sleep somewhere
this dangerous, right?

31
00:01:22,750 --> 00:01:25,119
Uh... no worries if that's inconvenient

32
00:01:25,120 --> 00:01:27,867
I'm kinda comfortable here too.

33
00:01:29,950 --> 00:01:32,392
Come to my place after class.

34
00:01:32,886 --> 00:01:35,715
See? Told you he's a good guy.

35
00:01:38,186 --> 00:01:41,068
Uh... thank you.

36
00:01:51,580 --> 00:01:54,149
Alright, have your assignments
turned in by next week,

37
00:01:54,150 --> 00:01:57,029
and that'll be all for today's class.

38
00:01:57,030 --> 00:01:59,753
Good work, everyone.

39
00:02:01,250 --> 00:02:02,775
Wanna work on the assignment together?

40
00:02:02,776 --> 00:02:04,339
The assignment?

41
00:02:04,340 --> 00:02:06,669
I figured it'd be better
if we did it together.

42
00:02:06,670 --> 00:02:09,636
Uh... sure.

43
00:02:23,130 --> 00:02:26,000
I think it'd look better if
this side had a lighter tone.

44
00:02:26,001 --> 00:02:28,861
And over here...

45
00:02:29,910 --> 00:02:32,189
Is it okay for you to keep helping me?

46
00:02:32,190 --> 00:02:33,869
What about your assignment...?

47
00:02:33,870 --> 00:02:36,702
Mm... it's fine.

48
00:02:36,703 --> 00:02:38,885
Should we blur this part a little more?

49
00:02:40,852 --> 00:02:41,982
Like this?

50
00:02:41,983 --> 00:02:43,897
Mm...

51
00:02:45,739 --> 00:02:47,839
If you do this part

52
00:02:47,840 --> 00:02:52,132
the same way as before,
it'll start looking too messy.

53
00:02:52,480 --> 00:02:54,269
Oh, okay.

54
00:02:54,270 --> 00:02:56,383
Wanna try it again?

55
00:02:57,251 --> 00:02:59,121
Yeah.

56
00:03:10,470 --> 00:03:14,434
Thank you, you really helped me a lot.

57
00:03:14,780 --> 00:03:16,769
How long have you been drawing?

58
00:03:16,770 --> 00:03:18,549
I've never really learned properly,

59
00:03:18,550 --> 00:03:20,733
I just doodle as a hobby...

60
00:03:20,734 --> 00:03:23,610
I didn't think it'd turn
out this good either...

61
00:03:27,641 --> 00:03:30,910
Huh? Oh, it's you from before...

62
00:03:32,213 --> 00:03:34,006
You know Hyunjun?

63
00:03:34,007 --> 00:03:35,080
Yeah.

64
00:03:35,081 --> 00:03:36,677
We just got acquainted recently.

65
00:03:36,678 --> 00:03:39,251
Ah, I see.

66
00:03:39,252 --> 00:03:40,994
Hi, nice seeing you again.

67
00:03:40,995 --> 00:03:43,076
Yeah, hi.

68
00:03:43,077 --> 00:03:45,379
Oh right!

69
00:03:48,596 --> 00:03:49,894
This is for you

70
00:03:49,895 --> 00:03:52,225
I still felt bad about
what happened that day.

71
00:03:52,226 --> 00:03:54,549
Ah, really, it's okay

72
00:03:54,550 --> 00:03:57,489
I was partly at fault too.

73
00:03:57,490 --> 00:03:59,299
Anyway, what are you doing here?

74
00:03:59,300 --> 00:04:00,709
Oh, nothing much

75
00:04:00,710 --> 00:04:02,441
I was helping him with an assignment.

76
00:04:02,442 --> 00:04:03,919
What about you?

77
00:04:03,920 --> 00:04:05,699
Me? I came to work on mine too.

78
00:04:05,700 --> 00:04:07,159
Wanna do it together?

79
00:04:07,160 --> 00:04:08,539
We just finished,

80
00:04:08,540 --> 00:04:12,399
so we'll get going first. Take your time.

81
00:04:43,236 --> 00:04:44,897
You two are friends?

82
00:04:44,899 --> 00:04:47,701
We're just classmates.

83
00:04:47,702 --> 00:04:50,469
Your friend seems really nice.

84
00:04:50,470 --> 00:04:51,857
Does he?

85
00:04:51,858 --> 00:04:54,340
Hyunjun!

86
00:04:55,942 --> 00:04:58,611
You left this behind.

87
00:04:58,612 --> 00:05:00,612
Oh, right.

88
00:05:17,972 --> 00:05:20,307
Excuse me.

89
00:05:20,308 --> 00:05:22,255
It's messy, but probably
better than school.

90
00:05:22,256 --> 00:05:23,389
Huh? No.

91
00:05:23,390 --> 00:05:25,371
It's really nice in here.

92
00:05:25,372 --> 00:05:27,740
You really live here alone?

93
00:05:27,741 --> 00:05:30,530
I'll get you something to change into.

94
00:05:56,437 --> 00:05:58,571
Not sure if it'll fit.

95
00:05:58,572 --> 00:06:00,499
Thank you.

96
00:06:00,500 --> 00:06:03,217
Want something to eat?

97
00:06:05,060 --> 00:06:07,267
What should we have?

98
00:06:15,388 --> 00:06:18,163
I don't really cook much at home...

99
00:06:18,164 --> 00:06:19,980
But this looks so good.

100
00:06:19,981 --> 00:06:22,121
Thank you for the meal.

101
00:06:35,155 --> 00:06:36,789
Slow down.

102
00:06:36,790 --> 00:06:39,546
Yeah, it's just so good...

103
00:06:41,520 --> 00:06:44,439
I heard you helped with
Yunghui's club poster too.

104
00:06:44,440 --> 00:06:46,239
Oh, yeah.

105
00:06:46,687 --> 00:06:49,739
Though I don't know if I
was actually much help.

106
00:06:49,740 --> 00:06:51,459
Oh right.

107
00:06:51,460 --> 00:06:54,939
How do you know Yunghui anyway?

108
00:06:54,940 --> 00:06:57,690
You two seem way too
different personality-wise.

109
00:06:59,145 --> 00:07:01,922
Since we were really little,
our parents were close friends,

110
00:07:01,923 --> 00:07:05,912
so we ended up going to the same
elementary, middle, and high school,

111
00:07:05,913 --> 00:07:08,595
and somehow even the same college...

112
00:07:08,596 --> 00:07:12,999
Ah... so you've known each other forever.

113
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:14,975
Sounds like he takes good care of you.

114
00:07:14,976 --> 00:07:16,303
Oh, definitely.

115
00:07:16,304 --> 00:07:18,638
Thanks to him,

116
00:07:18,639 --> 00:07:21,421
I think I've adjusted to
school life pretty well.

117
00:07:21,422 --> 00:07:23,422
That's good to hear.

118
00:07:31,044 --> 00:07:33,826
If it's too cramped, I
can sleep on the floor.

119
00:07:33,827 --> 00:07:35,189
If it's uncomfortable, I will.

120
00:07:35,190 --> 00:07:37,991
No... no, it's okay...

121
00:07:38,610 --> 00:07:40,827
Then let's just sleep like this.

122
00:07:45,290 --> 00:07:48,275
Who's the person in that
photo on the coffee table?

123
00:07:48,276 --> 00:07:50,296
You saw that?

124
00:07:50,297 --> 00:07:52,946
I was just looking around...

125
00:07:53,130 --> 00:07:54,373
My younger brother.

126
00:07:54,374 --> 00:07:55,969
Really?

127
00:07:55,970 --> 00:07:57,289
How old is he?

128
00:07:57,290 --> 00:08:00,169
By now, he'd just be an adult.

129
00:08:00,170 --> 00:08:02,235
Same age as you, probably.

130
00:08:04,261 --> 00:08:06,201
You must've been really close.

131
00:08:06,225 --> 00:08:07,500
We were.

132
00:08:07,501 --> 00:08:10,376
But he died in an accident.

133
00:08:14,090 --> 00:08:15,936
It's okay...

134
00:08:16,595 --> 00:08:19,011
I'm sorry... I shouldn't have...

135
00:08:20,752 --> 00:08:23,149
When I first lost my
brother in that accident,

136
00:08:23,150 --> 00:08:26,079
all I could think about was following him.

137
00:08:26,080 --> 00:08:27,829
He only had me,

138
00:08:27,830 --> 00:08:30,089
and I only had him.

139
00:08:30,090 --> 00:08:31,817
So I kept wondering if it was even right

140
00:08:31,818 --> 00:08:35,289
for me to smile and keep living my life.

141
00:08:35,290 --> 00:08:38,531
He must've been having
such a hard time without me...

142
00:08:39,652 --> 00:08:42,350
He's living happily

143
00:08:42,351 --> 00:08:44,938
I'm sure of it.

144
00:08:48,068 --> 00:08:49,249
Really.

145
00:08:49,250 --> 00:08:51,129
You don't believe me?

146
00:08:51,130 --> 00:08:53,526
Thank you.

147
00:08:54,147 --> 00:08:56,689
If I were your brother,

148
00:08:56,690 --> 00:09:00,960
I'd want my big brother to be happy.

149
00:09:02,080 --> 00:09:03,869
Live your life until then,

150
00:09:03,870 --> 00:09:05,879
and when you meet again someday,

151
00:09:05,880 --> 00:09:08,807
you'll have forever together then.

152
00:09:09,657 --> 00:09:11,870
I can't quite figure you out.

153
00:09:11,871 --> 00:09:13,871
Huh?

154
00:09:17,045 --> 00:09:18,400
When I first met you,

155
00:09:18,401 --> 00:09:21,030
I thought you were just some weird kid

156
00:09:21,031 --> 00:09:23,175
but somehow you feel really familiar too.

157
00:09:23,176 --> 00:09:26,719
Like just being around you is
comforting for some reason.

158
00:09:28,850 --> 00:09:31,571
Let's get closer.

159
00:09:38,986 --> 00:09:41,581
Okay.

